 they charge for an annual treatment of this type from 340,000 to 450,000 CZK. 

00:04:20.212 --> 00:04:24.900
 Given such a high price, I would hope that side effects will be hugs and rainbows. 

00:04:24.980 --> 00:04:28.180
 But that's not the case, these drugs carry a warning in a black box, 

00:04:28.184 --> 00:04:30.060
 because they can cause for example 

00:04:30.065 --> 00:04:32.790
 cancer and heart failure. 

00:04:32.790 --> 00:04:37.300
 If there were a cheaper and safer solution. 

00:04:37.304 --> 00:04:40.240
 Curcumin, yellow turmeric dye 

